data.description: INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY! This investment property features a spacious and updated 4 bedroom / 3 bath.  The bedrooms are well-appointed and offer ample storage space. In addition, there is an attached mother-in-law suite that offers a 1 bed/1 bath with its own private entrance. The home sits on a large 2.27-acre lot, providing plenty of space for outdoor activities and additional storage. There is also a metal RV shelter and a shed on the property, which could be used for various purposes, including an income source as well. The interior of the home has been tastefully updated, with modern fixtures and finishes throughout. There is more than one kitchen to accommodate the potential residents. The bathrooms have also been updated with modern fixtures and finishes. Overall, this investment property offers a unique opportunity for multiple renters or families to enjoy a comfortable and spacious home, with the added bonus of a large lot for room to roam.
